                     <origDate notBefore="1700" notAfter="1800">18th cent?
 In Additio 1, the
                        name of the king has been erased. The name of the king probably consisted of
                        some 4-5 letters: ኢዮአሰ or ዮሰጦሰ.</origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>Original names of donors have been erased and
                     sometimes replaced with that of Wälätta Śǝllāse (e.g., <locus target="#20va">20va</locus>, 24rb) in Additio 1 and the supplication formulas on <locus from="3ra" to="113vb">3ra-113vb</locus> (hand a). The names of Gabra Mikāʾel
                     and Walda Mikāʾel are written in the supplication formulas on <locus from="115ra" to="130vb">115ra-130vb</locus> (hand b).</provenance>
